application/control/initialize.php
will be included be included on Aplication::initialize()
(After environment is initialized and before controller is executed)

application/control/finalize.php
will be included be included on Aplication::finalize()
(Before environment is finalized and right after controller is executed)


application/control/routes.php
May contain routes (or "aliases") to map resources to controllers

E.G:
<?php
return array(
    'period' => array('Period_Controller', 'collection'),
    'period/:ID' => array('Period_Controller', 'single'),
    'period/:ID/period' => array('Period_Controller', 'collection'),

    'period/type' => array('Period_Type_Controller', 'collection'),
    'period/type/:ID' => array('Period_Type_Controller', 'single'),
    'period/type/:ID/period' => array('Period_Type_Controller', 'collection'),
);